Linode types
  10.04 LTE 64bits Ubuntu

Creating user 
  sudo adduser bar

Add user to sudo 
  visudo
  prod    ALL=(ALL) ALL

Change port of ssh
  /etc/ssh/sshd_config 
   Port 2202 

Disable root password
   sudo passwd -l root
  
Set authorized keys
   scp authorized_keys DRedis:~/.ssh/authorized_keys
